### Course - Update Course by ID
PUT {{API_HostAddress}}/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Introduction to Programming - Updated",
    "description": "Learn the basics of programming using Python. Updated content included.",
    "instructorId": "{{instructorId}}",
    "category": "Programming",
    "price": 59.99,
    "DurationInHours": 25
}

### Course - Delete Course by ID
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Course - Publish Course
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/courses/{{courseId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "publish": true
}

